ygData.messageBody:
Actually you can have a lot of fun even in the 40's in Ill Omen... If ya
like to swim :)

The goblins that drop the Coin and the nifty fish in there are blue to me at
41. There are some other things down there on track that I'm going to
investimigate eventually too...


Lyrnia the eternally (or is that terminally?) curious

> I cannot say this too many times. Lake of Ill Omen. This place is

>
> Kit
>
> Snip: If you need to convince yourself to go to kunark, talk to me.

> bubbles from 27. Where are some good places to go? I want Charm and

>
> Thanks,
